MuleDefinitionParser, MuleDefinitionParserConfiguration, org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.BeanDefinitionParser
public class TransportEndpointDefinitionParser
extends AddressedEndpointDefinitionParser

This is intended for use by endpoint-specific parsers for non-global endpoint elements.

It generates both an endpoint (which should subclass ImmutableEndpoint) and a URIBuilder. The URI is then injected into the endpoint. So the associated schema can enable any of the suitable ALL_ATTRIBUTES or add appropriate mappings.
